    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1866-12-27T23:59:59-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1866-12-27T00:00:00-05:00" n="224" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d224">
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Extract.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <head>
                    <persName type="from">Mr. Seward</persName> to <persName type="to">Mr.
                                Campbell</persName>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#left">No. 11.]</seg>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Department of State</hi>, <hi rend="italic">Washington,</hi>
                        </placeName>
                        <date calendar="gregorian" when="1866-12-27">
                            <hi rend="italic">December</hi> 27, 1866</date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>
                    <hi rend="smallcaps">Sir:</hi> I have to acknowledge the receipt of your
                            despatch of December 13, No. 6.</p>
                <p rend="center">* * * * * *</p>
                <p>Your proceedings at Vera Cruz, Tampico, and Brownsville, as therein
                            related, are approved.</p>
                <p>The information which you have given me is appreciated. With a
                            reservation, which I may take a more convenient occasion to mention, the
                            President approves of the notes of which a copy is appended to your
                            despatch.</p>
                <p>I am, sir, your obedient servant,</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>WILLIAM H. SEWARD,</signed>
                </closer>
                <postscript>
                    <p>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Lewis D. Campbell</hi>, Esq., <hi rend="italic">&amp;c., &amp;c., &amp;c.</hi>
                    </p>
                </postscript>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
